      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TRIVIA (8) impressed when posting a blistering 19.37 over 342m at Angle Park three back then has hit the frame in both runs since. Looks the one to beat on best figures. LOVING IT SWEET (6) has a strong record this journey here with two wins and a minor from six starts. Was out of the placings last time (26.26) at Murray Bridge in a Grade 5, finishing sixth and beaten 9 lengths. Looks well placed here and among the chances. PAW MANTRA (1) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (23.03) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Form at the trip sound including nine wins. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings five times from eight starts. Will give the top chances plenty to think about. REFERENT POWER (4) is last start winner who looks one of the chances.",
